item.title: Fire safety at home: How to prevent one of Australia's deadliest natural hazards
item.description: Home fire safety goes beyond having smoke alarms installed. In Australia, fatal residential fires are sadly common, despite being preventable. Here’s what you need to know to stop one from breaking out in your home. Feed: https://sbs-ondemand.streamguys1.com/settlement-guide/

item.title: Adolf Hitler vs Winston Churchill
item.description: Installed in Downing Street, Churchill arrives with a bang. The Battle of Britain rages in the skies, while the Nazis plot a seaborne invasion across the English Channel. And Hitler extends his network of allies, seeking to bring the Spanish and Japanese strongmen to the table… A Noiser production, written by Jeff Dawson. Scroll down the Real Dictators feed for episodes on Hitler’s early years and rise to power... Feed: https://feeds.megaphone.fm/NSR6187882468
